oading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">구성 요소</th>\n<th></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">Content</td>\n<td>콘텐츠가 표시되는 영역<br /> <code class=\"language-text\">width</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">height</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">Padding</td>\n<td>콘텐츠 주변의 여백 영역<br /><code class=\"language-text\">padding</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">Border</td>\n<td>콘텐츠와 패딩을 둘러싼 테두리 영역<br /><code class=\"language-text\">border</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">Margin</td>\n<td>콘텐츠, 패딩, 테두리를 둘러싼 가장 바깥 쪽 영역<br />다른 요소 사이의 공백 역할<br /><code class=\"language-text\">margin</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>박스의 실제 크기</p>\n<ul>\n<li>너비 = <code class=\"language-text\">border-left</code> + <code class=\"language-text\">padding-left</code> + <code class=\"language-text\">width</code> + <code class=\"language-text\">padding-right</code> + <code class=\"language-text\">border-right</code></li>\n<li>높이 = <code class=\"language-text\">border-top</code> + <code class=\"language-text\">padding-top</code> + <code class=\"language-text\">height</code> + <code class=\"language-text\">padding-bottom</code> + <code class=\"language-text\">border-bottom</code></li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">margin</code>은 박스의 외부 공간에 영향, 박스의 영역은 테두리에서 멈춤</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>box-sizing</h1>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">값</th>\n<th></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">content-box</td>\n<td>기본값<br />width, height 속성이 content 영역만 포함</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">border-box</td>\n<td>width, height 속성이 content, padding, border 영역을 포함<br />(margin 포함 X)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2>content-box</h2>\n<p><span\